This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Health Cloud or Life Sciences Cloud license. 

Pharmacy Benefits Verification is available starting in June 2024. This feature is available to users with the Health Cloud Foundation (for Health Cloud) or Health Cloud Starter (for Life Sciences Cloud), and Manage Pharmacy Benefits Verification permission set.

Add the PharmacyBenefitsVerification flexcard to the Care Program Enrollee record page.
